    "id": "L×W×H): 38.1 × 21.59 × 17.78 cm  Care & Safety Clean with a soft sponge and normal detergent, Do not use harsh chemicals or products to avoid scratches, Remove unwanted marks by rubbing the utensils with lemon .  Citizen – trusted Indian cookware engineered for safe, fast and flavorful cooking.  Durable Design and Material The Citizen pressure cooker is expertly designed with a smart copper matte finish, making it not only visually appealing but also very durable. This type of finish is resistant to scratches and tarnish, so it maintains its beauty over time. It is important to have cookware that lasts, and this cooker certainly delivers. Additionally, the inner lid is designed to maintain pressure effectively, ensuring optimal cooking results every time. You can rely on this product because it is built to last and perform.  Versatile Cooking Options This Citizen pressure cooker is compatible with both induction and gas stoves, providing flexibility in your cooking environment. Whether you prefer boiling, steaming, or pressure cooking, this cooker can handle it all. The ability to use it on different cooktops is a great advantage, especially for those who may switch between induction and gas. So, you can easily adapt your cooking style without worrying about compatibility issues.  Safety and Efficiency Safety is a big concern in cooking, and fortunately, the Citizen pressure cooker is ISI certified, which means it meets high safety standards. This cooker is equipped with advanced safety features that help protect users during operation. Because of these safety measures, you can cook faster with reduced energy consumption, leading to both time and cost savings in your kitchen. Therefore, the Citizen pressure cooker not only offers safety but also efficiency in your everyday cooking routine.    Smart Design Enhances Cooking Efficiency The Citizen pressure cooker features a smart design that combines convenience with efficiency. Its unique copper matte finish not only adds a stylish touch to your kitchen but also ensures quick heat conduction. Because this cooker is ISI certified, you can trust its quality and safety standards. Users have praised how fast they can prepare meals without sacrificing flavor or nutrition. So, if you're looking for a reliable cooking companion",
