    "tags": "its inner lid adds an extra layer of safety and helps maintain optimal pressure levels while cooking. This ensures that your meals are cooked evenly and efficiently",
    "name": "saving you time and effort in the kitchen.  User-Friendly Features for Everyday Cooking The Citizen pressure cooker is not just about looks; it's packed with user-friendly features that make everyday cooking easier. The stainless steel lid facilitates easy opening and locking, ensuring a secure seal during cooking. As a result, you can cook with confidence knowing that the steam is trapped inside to enhance flavor and tenderness. This pressure cooker also allows for various cooking techniques, such as steaming or sautéing, providing flexibility for all your culinary adventures.",
